product.name: Coaster Home Furnishings - Marbrisa - Asian Hardwood - Set of 2 Wood Dining Side Chairs with Tall Slatted Backs, Scooped Seats and Mission-Style Design - Dining Room and Kitchen - Matte Black - 123072
product.description: Blending heritage charm with modern versatility, these black wood dining chairs feature a refined mission-style design, gently scooped seats, and structured tall slatted backs that offer support with timeless appeal. Crafted from durable Asian hardwood construction and coated in a sleek matte black finish, they bring visual depth to any dining room or casual nook. Perfect as kitchen dining chairs, this set of 2 dining chairs functions beautifully as armless side chairs within transitional layouts or formal arrangements. Designed to complement home furnishing styles both rustic and modern, these wood dining side chairs deliver lasting value with clean straight profiles and a non-upholstered silhouette that defines classic transitional style. Dimensions: Side Chair Seat Dimensions: 17.75 inches high x 19.5 inches wide x 16.75 inches deep
product.bullet_points:
• Includes: Two (2) side chairs
• [Timeless craftsmanship for everyday use] These black wood dining chairs are built with durable Asian hardwood construction and shaped with scooped seats to provide lasting comfort and strength in both casual and formal spaces.
• [Clean lines meet classic charm] Featuring tall slatted backs, straight profiles, and a nod to mission-style design, these non upholstered chairs bring heritage-inspired detail into transitional homes.
• [Versatile form for multiple settings] Designed as armless side chairs, this set of 2 dining chairs works equally well in compact nooks or large gatherings, complementing both kitchen dining spaces and mixed-material layouts.
• [Neutral tones for easy pairing] Featuring a sleek matte black finish, these wood dining side chairs integrate beautifully into a variety of home furnishing aesthetics, from earthy textures to polished interiors.
• [Built to balance comfort and structure] A smart fit for the dining room, this pair adds polish to your furniture while supporting open-concept living with a subtle transitional style that blends function and form.
